name: Emoji Mega Pack (3,900 iOS Apple Emojis)
description:
Emoji Mega Pack (Free)

Full iOS Library | More Great Figma Resources


3,900+ Apple emojis organized, labeled and usable as Figma components. Up to date with the latest iOS release.


All emojis are 72x72, compressed PNGs, to keep the file size as reasonable as possible.


🪄Skin tone options included for applicable emojis.


Organized into 8 categories

🥰 Smileys & People

🦊 Animals & Nature

🍓 Food & Drink

🏂 Activity

🏖️ Travel & Places

🎈 Objects

💯 Symbols

🏳️‍🌈 Flags


♾️ Free for the Figma Community. Enjoy!
